<paragraph blockId="20.[112,648,369,525]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345">
DISTRIBUTION. — This species is mainly a forest-dweller. It had been recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[383,433,395,419]" name="Togo" pageId="20" pageNumber="345">Togo</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="MATSCHIE P." box="[473,641,395,419]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345" pagination="207 - 215" refId="ref28100" refString="MATSCHIE P. 1893. - Die Reptilien und Amphibien Togogebietes. Mittheilungen von Forschungsreisenden und Gelehrten aus den deutschen Schutzgebieten, mit Benutzung amtlicher Quellen 6: 207 - 215." type="journal article" year="1893">Matschie (1893)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="STERNFELD L." box="[115,284,422,446]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345" pagination="207 - 236" refId="ref29004" refString="STERNFELD L. 1908 b. - Die Schlangenfauna Togos. Mittheilungen Zoologischen Museum in Berlin 4: 207 - 236." type="journal article" year="1908">Sternfeld (1908b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="STERNFELD L." box="[296,350,422,446]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345" refId="ref29026" refString="STERNFELD L. 1909. - Die Schlangen Togos, in Die Fauna der deutschen Kolonien 1 (1): iv + 29 p., map." type="book" year="1909">1909</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation author="LOVERIDGE A." box="[369,535,422,446]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345" pagination="121 - 247" refId="ref27999" refString="LOVERIDGE A. 1944. - Further revisions of African snake genera. Bulletin of the the Museum of Comparative Zoology 95: 121 - 247." type="journal article" year="1944">Loveridge (1944</bibRefCitation>
; from Missahohe), and 
<bibRefCitation author="HULSELMANS J. L. J. &amp; VERHEYEN W. N." box="[247,568,448,472]" pageId="20" pageNumber="345" pagination="200 - 204" refId="ref27452" refString="HULSELMANS J. L. J. &amp; VERHEYEN W. N. 1970. - Contribution a l'herpetologie de la Republique du Togo: Liste preliminaire des serpents recoltes par la deuxieme mission zoologique belge au Togo. Revue de Zoologie et de Botanique africaines 82 (1 - 2): 200 - 204." type="journal article" year="1970">Hulselmans &amp; Verheyen (1970)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="LEACHE A. D. &amp; RODEL M. - O. &amp; LINKEM C. W. &amp; DIAZ R. E. &amp; HILLERS A. &amp; FUJITA M. K." pageId="20" pageNumber="345" pagination="22 - 45" refId="ref27816" refString="LEACHE A. D., RODEL M. - O., LINKEM C. W., DIAZ R. E., HILLERS A. &amp; FUJITA M. K. 2006. - Biodiversity in a forest island: reptiles and amphibians of the West African Togo hills. Amphibian and Reptile Conservation 4: 22 - 45." type="journal article" year="2006">
Leaché 
<emphasis box="[115,159,474,498]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="345">et al.</emphasis>
(2006)
</bibRefCitation>
also mentioned the occurrence of the species in the forest area between 
<collectingCountry box="[367,432,501,525]" name="Ghana" pageId="20" pageNumber="345">Ghana</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[480,533,501,525]" name="Togo" pageId="20" pageNumber="345">Togo</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
